---
title: Bacon, Courgette & Corn Fritters with Roast Pumpkin Salad & Smokey Aioli
description: These sweet and salty fritters are the perfect marriage of tasty ingredients and easy cooking techniques. With bacon in the fritter mix and smokey aioli served on the side, this crowd-pleasing meal will be devoured in record time!
